# Task 1: Basic SQL Queries – Employees DB

This folder contains Task 1 for my SQL practice series based on the `employees` dataset from the [datacharmer/test_db](https://github.com/datacharmer/test_db) repository.

##  What I Did

- Set up MySQL using test_db dataset (~2.8M rows)
- Ran 12+ core queries using:
  - `SELECT` columns
  - `WHERE`, `BETWEEN`, `LIKE`
  - `ORDER BY`, `LIMIT`, `OFFSET`
  - Pattern matching and data validation

##  Files

- `SQL_Task_1_Queries.sql` – All SQL queries
- `SQL_Task_1_Report.docx` – Report with explanations
- `screenshots/` – Screenshots showing query output in CLI

##  Sample Queries

sql
SELECT emp_no, salary, salary * 1.10 AS increased_salary
FROM salaries
LIMIT 10;
